64bfc99e6fdea04ecb512bc3dea05e55f5478654.query:
insert into repository (name, name_with_owner, license, stars, primary_language, languages, created_at)
values ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
on conflict (name)
do update
set name = $1,
    name_with_owner = $2,
    license = $3,
    stars = $4,
    primary_language = $5,
    languages = $6,
    created_at = $7
